OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FAston born Rock and roll legend Ozzy
OL,8,FOsbourne is going to be given a
OL,9,Fposthumous lifetime achievement award
OL,10,Fat tomorrow's Brit Awards.
OL,12,FOne of the founding members and
OL,13,Ffrontman of Black Sabbath will be
OL,14,Fhonoured in recognition and
OL,15,Fcelebration of this impact and
OL,16,Finfluence to rock music worldwide.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
