OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772478695
OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FDescribed as a pioneering 'godfather'
OL,8,Fof British heavy metal, Ozzy Osbourne
OL,9,Fdied on 22nd July 2025 at the age of
OL,10,F76, having been diagnosed with
OL,11,FParkinson's disease in 2019.
OL,13,FHis wife, Sharon Osbourne, has
OL,14,Forganised an all-star rock tribute
OL,15,Fperformance during the ceremony, which
OL,16,Fwill be fronted by Stoke-on-Trent's
OL,17,FRobbie Williams.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772478695
OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FThe performance will be a special
OL,8,Farrangement of 'No More Tears' - the
OL,9,Ftitle track from Ozzy's multi-million
OL,10,Fselling 1991 album of the same name.
OL,12,FMusicians who will be part of the
OL,13,Fperformance include those who have
OL,14,Fplayed a part of Ozzy's band over the
OL,15,Fyears, including Adam Wakeman, Tommy
OL,16,FClufetos, Zakk Wylde and Robert
OL,17,FTrujillo from Metallica.
OL,19,FThe Osbourne family are no strangers
OL,20,Fto The BRIT Awards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
