PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772478695
OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FOzzy hosted the awards in 2008, along
OL,8,Fwith his family Sharon, Kelly and Jack.
OL,10,FBlack Sabbath's eponymous debut album
OL,11,Fin 1970 made the UK top 10 and paved
OL,12,Fthe way for a string of hit records.
OL,14,FThey went on to become one of the most
OL,15,Finfluential and successful metal bands
OL,16,Fof all time, selling more than 75
OL,17,Fmillion albums worldwide.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
