PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772478695
OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FThe group were inducted into the Rock
OL,8,FAnd Roll Hall of Fame in 2006, and
OL,9,FOsbourne was added for a second time
OL,10,Fin 2024.
OL,12,FIn July 2025, thousands of fans
OL,13,Fvisited the Black Sabbath Bench on
OL,14,FBroad Street in the musician's home
OL,15,Fcity to lay bouquets, wreaths,
OL,16,Fposters, balloons, candles and cards,
OL,17,Fand line the street for his public
OL,18,Ffuneral procession.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
