PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772478695
OL,3,COzzy Osbourne to get posthumous
OL,4,Clifetime achievement award at Brit
OL,5,Cawards
OL,7,FHis death came only a few weeks after
OL,8,Fthe band's Back to the Beginning
OL,9,Fconcert at Villa Park, where the band
OL,10,Fcelebrated its roots and connection to
OL,11,FBirmingham.
OL,13,FThe 2026 BRIT Awards will be live on
OL,14,FITV1 and ITVX from 8:15pm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
